1
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,918
=Vanished Name=

2
00:01:35,256 --> 00:01:37,592
=Episode 27=
(Meeting Halfway)

3
00:01:54,090 --> 00:01:55,211
I'm going to kill her.

4
00:01:56,450 --> 00:01:57,211
You die first.

5
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:13,912
(Demolish)

6
00:03:29,170 --> 00:03:30,890
It's been hours since she got back.

7
00:03:31,210 --> 00:03:32,770
What is she pacing around for?

8
00:03:34,291 --> 00:03:35,210
Is she taking a walk?

9
00:03:41,371 --> 00:03:43,650
Mama Bear and Baby Bear

10
00:03:43,930 --> 00:03:47,730
lived happily ever after together.

11
00:03:48,152 --> 00:03:49,560
(Huang Zhiqiang)

12
00:04:00,312 --> 00:04:01,688
(Huang Zhiqiang)

13
00:04:30,931 --> 00:04:31,450
Hello?

14
00:04:32,691 --> 00:04:34,330
Didn't I tell you not to contact me

15
00:04:35,171 --> 00:04:36,330
but wait for me to call you?

16
00:04:37,890 --> 00:04:40,290
I know what you did to me.

17
00:04:41,174 --> 00:04:42,744
Meet me at the reservoir in 15 minutes.

18
00:04:43,890 --> 00:04:46,611
Otherwise, you'll never find me again.

19
00:05:55,650 --> 00:05:58,491
Back then,
you hid the poison in the pastry

20
00:05:59,611 --> 00:06:02,691
and made me kill someone
with my car, didn't you?

21
00:06:06,970 --> 00:06:10,011
What happened in the past is settled.

22
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:12,371
Now, other than cooperating with me,

23
00:06:13,530 --> 00:06:14,770
you have no other way out.

24
00:06:22,251 --> 00:06:23,330
As long as I'm here,

25
00:06:24,530 --> 00:06:25,731
you're in the clear.

26
00:06:27,691 --> 00:06:29,811
I'll always be your shield.

27
00:06:32,051 --> 00:06:33,090
Don't talk nonsense.

28
00:06:42,931 --> 00:06:45,171
You're doing it
for Bai Shu and Ren Xiaoming too.

29
00:06:46,530 --> 00:06:48,090
They're your friends.

30
00:06:51,850 --> 00:06:54,410
I always thought I was helping them.

31
00:06:55,650 --> 00:06:57,131
But only today did I realize

32
00:06:58,731 --> 00:07:00,371
that by using me to do those things,

33
00:07:01,770 --> 00:07:03,890
you've kept Bai Shu
under your control all along.

34
00:07:04,931 --> 00:07:06,051
I wasn't helping them.

35
00:07:07,731 --> 00:07:10,410
Instead, I destroyed them.

36
00:07:23,691 --> 00:07:24,691
Don't think that way.

37
00:07:28,131 --> 00:07:30,051
The police don't have any evidence now.

38
00:07:31,931 --> 00:07:33,931
It will likely become an unsolved case.

39
00:07:34,970 --> 00:07:37,571
They'll never find evidence
in this lifetime.

40
00:07:38,410 --> 00:07:39,890
We'll both be fine.

41
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:45,931
I don't know if others will be okay,

42
00:07:48,090 --> 00:07:50,890
but no one will take the fall for you.

43
00:08:07,850 --> 00:08:08,491
Zhang Fang?

44
00:08:11,970 --> 00:08:13,731
Zhang Fang fell in the water.
Send rescue.

45
00:08:16,210 --> 00:08:17,931
Zhang... Zhang Fang?

46
00:08:18,330 --> 00:08:19,131
Zhang Fang?

47
00:08:21,011 --> 00:08:21,770
Zhang Fang?

48
00:08:28,890 --> 00:08:29,592
No.

49
00:09:14,290 --> 00:09:16,376
Shun?

50
00:09:17,050 --> 00:09:19,570
It's almost 2 AM.
Why is she still pacing around?

51
00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:22,851
Something's off.

52
00:09:24,530 --> 00:09:25,211
Let's go.

53
00:09:44,890 --> 00:09:47,451
Captain Li, we lost Bai Shu.

54
00:10:48,650 --> 00:10:49,491
Zhang Fang is dead.

55
00:10:51,930 --> 00:10:52,690
It was you.

56
00:10:55,491 --> 00:10:57,050
You made him die.

57
00:10:58,810 --> 00:11:01,690
Back then, it was you
who put the sedative in the pastry.

58
00:11:03,211 --> 00:11:05,851
It was also you who made Zhang Fang
put the pastry in the car.

59
00:11:07,331 --> 00:11:10,131
I didn't kill him. You did.

60
00:11:12,971 --> 00:11:15,131
He was just your scapegoat.

61
00:11:16,611 --> 00:11:17,650
What scapegoat?

62
00:11:19,290 --> 00:11:20,770
I don't know what you mean.

63
00:11:33,211 --> 00:11:34,131
Zhang Fang is dead.

64
00:11:34,580 --> 00:11:36,180
About the thing you used to threaten me,

65
00:11:36,690 --> 00:11:38,251
I doubt you'd hand it to the police.

66
00:11:38,810 --> 00:11:40,091
For Ren Xiaoming,

67
00:11:41,211 --> 00:11:42,650
you even drove someone

68
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:46,371
who loved you so much to death.

69
00:11:49,570 --> 00:11:50,570
You're ruthless.

70
00:11:55,611 --> 00:11:57,170
The truth will come out one day.

71
00:11:58,091 --> 00:11:59,251
Your magic is gone.

72
00:12:00,530 --> 00:12:01,611
I'm leaving.

73
00:12:03,491 --> 00:12:04,491
I'll take Xiaoyu with me.

74
00:12:18,211 --> 00:12:20,731
Judgment is just beginning.

75
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:56,170
Sir, to the airport.

76
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:04,890
Please drive faster.

77
00:13:31,096 --> 00:13:33,176
(A Hundred Years of Divergence)

78
00:13:48,472 --> 00:13:49,688
(Network Is Unavailable, Shu)

79
00:13:56,091 --> 00:13:57,290
Here's what you wanted.

80
00:14:01,851 --> 00:14:04,251
You must promise me
you'll keep your word.

81
00:14:18,936 --> 00:14:19,896
(Shu)

82
00:14:20,024 --> 00:14:21,784
(My Favorites)

83
00:14:21,848 --> 00:14:24,824
(Notes)

84
00:14:34,072 --> 00:14:35,160
(Shu)

85
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:36,472
(A Hundred Years of Divergence)

86
00:14:40,792 --> 00:14:43,384
(Care about the kids)

87
00:14:45,944 --> 00:14:47,288
(I want to...)

88
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:53,752
(I want to entrust Xiaoyu...)

89
00:15:03,736 --> 00:15:06,872
(I want to entrust Xiaoyu to you)

90
00:15:10,648 --> 00:15:13,944
(Shu)

91
00:15:17,592 --> 00:15:22,840
(Send)

92
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:28,216
(Flight Number)

93
00:15:31,416 --> 00:15:33,432
(Arrival Time 10:19, Seat 21L)

94
00:15:43,011 --> 00:15:43,530
Hello?

95
00:15:44,091 --> 00:15:45,810
Ge Wenjun said Bai Shu took Xiaoyu away.

96
00:15:46,131 --> 00:15:48,170
Find them.
Tell me immediately if there's news.

97
00:15:48,371 --> 00:15:48,984
Okay.

98
00:16:04,331 --> 00:16:05,290
I'm sorry.

99
00:16:15,011 --> 00:16:15,731
Thank you.

100
00:16:24,011 --> 00:16:25,611
You must do what you promised me.

101
00:16:29,690 --> 00:16:30,371
Okay.

102
00:17:09,576 --> 00:17:16,376
(Psychiatry General Ward)

103
00:17:21,651 --> 00:17:22,651
Sir, to the airport.

104
00:17:23,491 --> 00:17:24,610
Drive faster, please.

105
00:17:24,770 --> 00:17:25,290
Okay.

106
00:18:27,090 --> 00:18:28,290
Our fault. Poor oversight.

107
00:18:28,971 --> 00:18:30,810
The personnel involved
have been suspended.

108
00:18:43,896 --> 00:18:45,240
(A Hundred Years of Divergence)

109
00:18:53,451 --> 00:18:54,810
(The master copy might be a book.)

110
00:19:02,491 --> 00:19:03,651
Please hold this for me.

111
00:19:09,112 --> 00:19:09,651
(Details)

112
00:19:09,651 --> 00:19:10,610
101925.

113
00:19:16,891 --> 00:19:18,130
371512.

114
00:19:25,688 --> 00:19:27,128
(No)

115
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:35,000
(Name)

116
00:19:36,530 --> 00:19:39,050
Add me now, or I'll turn myself in.

117
00:19:40,530 --> 00:19:41,770
The unidentified deceased

118
00:19:42,411 --> 00:19:43,731
knew the truth.

119
00:19:45,330 --> 00:19:47,211
The unidentified deceased
knew the truth.

120
00:19:48,251 --> 00:19:50,770
She even spent money on the dead.

121
00:19:51,731 --> 00:19:54,171
She also bought a plot
at Wuming Mountain Cemetery.

122
00:19:54,891 --> 00:19:56,171
(Unidentified deceased.)
[*"Unidentified" pronounced as "Wu Ming" in Chinese]

123
00:19:57,171 --> 00:19:57,971
Wuming Mountain?

124
00:20:00,011 --> 00:20:00,651
Thank you.

125
00:20:09,971 --> 00:20:10,691
Hello? Ma'am.

126
00:20:10,931 --> 00:20:13,931
Go check out the grave plot
Ren Xiaoming bought at Wuming Mountain.

127
00:20:14,011 --> 00:20:14,530
Yes.

128
00:20:19,850 --> 00:20:22,770
Captain Li, I found out Bai Shu
booked a flight ticket to Qingzhou.

129
00:20:22,971 --> 00:20:23,850
Plane's taken off.

130
00:20:23,850 --> 00:20:24,731
It lands at 10:19.

131
00:20:25,651 --> 00:20:27,931
Contact the Qingzhou police
to cooperate with us.

132
00:20:28,451 --> 00:20:29,048
Okay.

133
00:20:33,560 --> 00:20:37,624
(Domestic Departures)

134
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,368
(Domestic Arrivals, West Exit)

135
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:09,171
Please wait.

136
00:21:09,656 --> 00:21:10,360
(Police)

137
00:21:10,931 --> 00:21:11,891
Are you Ren Xiaoming?

138
00:21:12,250 --> 00:21:14,410
I'm with Qingzhou Police's
Criminal Investigation Unit.

139
00:21:14,691 --> 00:21:16,810
You're now
under criminal detention by law.

140
00:21:26,392 --> 00:21:28,376
(Zhao Xiaoyu)

141
00:21:47,731 --> 00:21:49,011
(I won't be able to escape.)

142
00:21:50,330 --> 00:21:52,370
(I bought you and Xiaofei
two apartments)

143
00:21:53,610 --> 00:21:54,931
and saved some money for you.

144
00:21:55,731 --> 00:21:56,931
Don't waste that money.

145
00:21:57,731 --> 00:21:58,850
Don't give it to anyone.

146
00:22:00,810 --> 00:22:02,491
If you're unsure about anything,

147
00:22:03,770 --> 00:22:05,050
just give Liang Yi a call.

148
00:22:06,731 --> 00:22:07,251
Liang Yi,

149
00:22:09,491 --> 00:22:10,570
please take care of them.

150
00:22:11,512 --> 00:22:14,491
(Zhao Xiaoyu)

151
00:22:14,491 --> 00:22:15,931
(If anyone dares to bully you,)

152
00:22:17,171 --> 00:22:17,891
(go find Li Meng.)

153
00:22:19,731 --> 00:22:21,211
(Although she might arrest me,)

154
00:22:22,530 --> 00:22:23,691
(that's her job.)

155
00:22:24,651 --> 00:22:25,370
(Don't blame her.)

156
00:22:29,610 --> 00:22:30,232
Mom,

157
00:22:32,050 --> 00:22:33,451
I want to ask you for one thing.

158
00:22:35,651 --> 00:22:37,330
If you see me get arrested,

159
00:22:39,171 --> 00:22:39,850
don't cry.

160
00:22:40,984 --> 00:22:43,768
(Zhao Xiaoyu)

161
00:23:25,011 --> 00:23:28,251
Could you open the window?

162
00:23:28,251 --> 00:23:28,891
It's stuffy.

163
00:23:31,130 --> 00:23:32,691
Zheng, open the window a bit.

164
00:23:39,770 --> 00:23:40,472
Meng,

165
00:23:42,610 --> 00:23:43,330
I'm sorry.

166
00:23:50,451 --> 00:23:51,451
In another 20 years,

167
00:23:52,610 --> 00:23:53,530
where will we be?

168
00:23:55,691 --> 00:23:57,011
Will we remember this?

169
00:24:19,691 --> 00:24:20,370
(Don't cry.)

170
00:24:22,891 --> 00:24:24,411
(Today is the easiest day)

171
00:24:26,130 --> 00:24:27,491
(in so many years.)

172
00:24:43,090 --> 00:24:46,491
Ma'am, we found Ren Xiaoming's diary
at the Wuming Mountain cemetery.

173
00:24:46,651 --> 00:24:47,891
Okay. What about Bai Shu?

174
00:24:48,050 --> 00:24:48,691
Any news?

175
00:24:48,810 --> 00:24:49,370
Still looking.

176
00:24:50,570 --> 00:24:51,570
Ren Xiaoming is detained.

177
00:24:51,850 --> 00:24:52,931
Bai Shu is craftier.

178
00:24:53,211 --> 00:24:53,850
We must get her.

179
00:24:54,330 --> 00:24:56,011
All her usual spots are covered.

180
00:24:58,648 --> 00:24:59,931
(La City Police)

181
00:24:59,931 --> 00:25:02,011
Bai Shu, Ren Xiaoming told me
to wait here for you.

182
00:25:02,411 --> 00:25:03,931
I'm her friend, Liang Yi.

183
00:25:06,530 --> 00:25:07,931
Falsely confessing for someone

184
00:25:07,931 --> 00:25:09,570
to help them escape justice

185
00:25:09,570 --> 00:25:10,491
means jail time.

186
00:25:11,451 --> 00:25:12,850
Ren Xiaoming didn't get Xiaoyu.

187
00:25:13,272 --> 00:25:14,491
She told me to await you here.

188
00:25:14,931 --> 00:25:15,931
Let's talk elsewhere.

189
00:25:17,891 --> 00:25:19,891
The three of us checked three times.

190
00:25:19,931 --> 00:25:22,290
The content in the novel
and the diary are the same.

191
00:25:22,610 --> 00:25:24,891
Especially the last chapter,
Leopard and Graveyard.

192
00:25:25,171 --> 00:25:26,330
(Breathe)
They're identical.

193
00:25:27,530 --> 00:25:29,570
(So the diary was indeed
in Ren Xiaoming's hands.)

194
00:25:30,691 --> 00:25:32,411
(The diary doesn't say
she's the killer.)

195
00:25:32,731 --> 00:25:34,570
(Why would she hide the diary away?)

196
00:25:35,451 --> 00:25:37,570
(Bai Shu had been guiding me
to get the diary.)

197
00:25:38,171 --> 00:25:40,290
(But there's nothing incriminating
about her in it.)

198
00:25:41,810 --> 00:25:43,211
(What are they two)

199
00:25:43,530 --> 00:25:45,330
(really playing at with this diary?)

200
00:25:49,610 --> 00:25:51,011
Ma'am, it's time.

201
00:25:52,810 --> 00:25:53,370
Bring her.

202
00:25:53,530 --> 00:25:54,090
Okay.

203
00:26:00,570 --> 00:26:03,130
The reason I got Xiaoming
out of the mental hospital

204
00:26:03,651 --> 00:26:04,931
was to let her turn herself in.

205
00:26:05,651 --> 00:26:06,530
She promised me that.

206
00:26:06,770 --> 00:26:09,211
But for your sake,
she didn't go straight to the police.

207
00:26:10,651 --> 00:26:11,891
What we can do now

208
00:26:12,610 --> 00:26:14,451
is make her tell the truth.

209
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:17,330
I'm the one who should tell the truth.

210
00:26:18,810 --> 00:26:19,610
What did you say?

211
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:23,211
Then I'll just tell the police.

212
00:26:23,211 --> 00:26:24,011
What will you say?

213
00:26:25,891 --> 00:26:29,050
Ren Xiaoming is lying.
I am the murderer.

214
00:26:31,971 --> 00:26:33,090
I am the murderer

215
00:26:33,931 --> 00:26:35,651
you've been looking for all along.

216
00:26:40,491 --> 00:26:42,891
Describe your crime in detail.

217
00:26:48,152 --> 00:26:48,971
(2010, Qidaohezi)

218
00:26:48,971 --> 00:26:50,691
(On August 10, 2010,)

219
00:26:51,491 --> 00:26:53,491
(I returned to Qidaohezi from Qingzhou)

220
00:26:53,491 --> 00:26:55,731
- Come take a look!
- (to meet an old friend.)

221
00:26:55,731 --> 00:26:57,290
Stop by! Have a seat!

222
00:26:58,011 --> 00:27:00,011
- (I was rushing to the spot.)
- Rice noodle rolls!

223
00:27:00,570 --> 00:27:01,570
(But then my mom saw me.)

224
00:27:01,570 --> 00:27:02,491
Rice noodle rolls!

225
00:27:03,171 --> 00:27:04,850
Fresh pork-filled rice noodle rolls!

226
00:27:05,451 --> 00:27:06,370
Ren Xiaoming!

227
00:27:07,770 --> 00:27:09,211
Ren Xiaoming, stop right there!

228
00:27:09,530 --> 00:27:10,130
Mom!

229
00:27:10,130 --> 00:27:11,130
When did you get back?

230
00:27:11,850 --> 00:27:13,130
Why didn't you come home?

231
00:27:13,251 --> 00:27:14,570
Can I talk to you later?

232
00:27:15,130 --> 00:27:15,931
What are you doing?

233
00:27:16,171 --> 00:27:17,290
Are you still with him?

234
00:27:17,451 --> 00:27:18,610
Did you come to see him?

235
00:27:20,050 --> 00:27:21,491
Did you go see that guy again?

236
00:27:21,491 --> 00:27:22,290
Where is He Yuqiong?

237
00:27:22,290 --> 00:27:22,931
I'm seeing him.

238
00:27:22,931 --> 00:27:23,651
So what?

239
00:27:23,651 --> 00:27:24,770
I just like him. I just do.

240
00:27:24,770 --> 00:27:25,530
I just want him.

241
00:27:25,530 --> 00:27:27,050
I'm not a kid. Why can't I date?

242
00:27:27,251 --> 00:27:28,090
I study well.

243
00:27:28,090 --> 00:27:29,130
Why can't I date?

244
00:27:29,130 --> 00:27:30,691
Your future is my business.

245
00:27:30,691 --> 00:27:31,731
Leave me alone.

246
00:27:31,731 --> 00:27:33,251
You won't listen until you fall.

247
00:27:37,251 --> 00:27:37,891
Ren Xiaoming!

248
00:27:37,891 --> 00:27:39,211
Waitress, is it ready yet?

249
00:27:41,451 --> 00:27:43,731
(I was almost late
because she stopped me.)

250
00:27:44,536 --> 00:27:45,130
(Friendship Forever Eatery)

251
00:27:45,130 --> 00:27:46,050
(I was in a hurry.)

252
00:28:05,171 --> 00:28:06,610
(I planned to tap the window.)

253
00:28:07,530 --> 00:28:10,090
(But then I decided to surprise him.)

254
00:28:10,810 --> 00:28:12,810
(I ran toward the eatery entrance.)

255
00:28:17,330 --> 00:28:20,931
(At that moment
I saw a familiar figure.)

256
00:28:22,770 --> 00:28:23,491
Zhou Na?

257
00:28:25,731 --> 00:28:27,290
(She was holding a knife.)

258
00:28:27,570 --> 00:28:28,251
Shameless!

259
00:28:28,651 --> 00:28:30,530
I'll slap you dead! You homewrecker!

260
00:28:31,290 --> 00:28:33,810
(I recalled what she did to Bai Shu.)

261
00:28:36,130 --> 00:28:37,570
(I had an ominous feeling.)

262
00:28:40,931 --> 00:28:42,610
(I didn't have time to greet him.)

263
00:28:43,530 --> 00:28:44,850
(I followed Zhou Na.)

264
00:28:47,810 --> 00:28:49,931
I followed her to Rest Cemetery.

265
00:28:53,651 --> 00:28:56,411
As expected, she went to harm Bai Shu.

266
00:29:12,530 --> 00:29:13,171
Xiaoming!

267
00:29:45,330 --> 00:29:47,411
The leopard
was Zhou Na in leopard print.

268
00:29:48,570 --> 00:29:50,171
The branch was the pen.

269
00:29:51,251 --> 00:29:53,451
The dove on the branch was the soul.

270
00:29:56,810 --> 00:29:58,130
The soul flew away.

271
00:29:59,931 --> 00:30:00,891
Zhou Na died.

272
00:30:02,770 --> 00:30:06,251
How did the body enter
the Qidian Middle School's statue base?

273
00:30:08,891 --> 00:30:10,011
I really don't know.

274
00:30:11,451 --> 00:30:13,411
We never went back to that forest.

275
00:30:17,971 --> 00:30:19,770
Ren Xiaofei's medical records

276
00:30:21,370 --> 00:30:22,651
and billing details.

277
00:30:23,050 --> 00:30:24,850
Did you upload
all these online yourself?

278
00:30:25,491 --> 00:30:26,011
Yes.

279
00:30:27,931 --> 00:30:28,850
The video reporters got

280
00:30:29,451 --> 00:30:32,211
about you going crazy at home
was also sent by you?

281
00:30:34,850 --> 00:30:35,451
Yes.

282
00:30:36,850 --> 00:30:38,411
After the psychiatric evaluation,

283
00:30:38,691 --> 00:30:40,090
you'd gain a life-saving charm.

284
00:30:42,451 --> 00:30:43,090
Yes.

285
00:30:44,411 --> 00:30:45,731
You suspected Bai Shu

286
00:30:45,931 --> 00:30:48,691
might give us clues about the diary.

287
00:30:49,130 --> 00:30:51,610
So you used the copyright trial

288
00:30:52,171 --> 00:30:53,491
to deny the diary's existence.

289
00:30:54,050 --> 00:30:54,691
Yes.

290
00:30:55,330 --> 00:30:56,211
To get off the hook,

291
00:30:57,011 --> 00:30:59,451
you used the copyright case
to deny the diary

292
00:30:59,850 --> 00:31:01,411
and then used media for publicity,

293
00:31:02,171 --> 00:31:04,130
portraying yourself as mentally ill.

294
00:31:04,731 --> 00:31:06,130
You divorced to leave a way out

295
00:31:06,850 --> 00:31:08,530
and used the guise of asset transfer

296
00:31:08,931 --> 00:31:10,770
to leave family
money and properties, right?

297
00:31:13,570 --> 00:31:14,251
Yes.

298
00:31:17,251 --> 00:31:20,290
Did you make Liu Xiaoran
publish this novel under his name?

299
00:31:21,691 --> 00:31:23,370
You want to know

300
00:31:24,891 --> 00:31:26,570
if Liu Xiaoran is an accomplice

301
00:31:28,171 --> 00:31:31,330
and if publishing the novel
is part of my exoneration plan,

302
00:31:32,850 --> 00:31:33,451
right?

303
00:31:33,850 --> 00:31:36,411
I'm asking you. Answer truthfully.

304
00:31:39,171 --> 00:31:41,330
He's just a selfish, greedy fool.

305
00:31:42,330 --> 00:31:43,530
How could he possibly know?

306
00:31:44,491 --> 00:31:45,770
It has nothing to do with him.

307
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:49,330
It has nothing to do with anyone.

308
00:31:51,491 --> 00:31:52,651
I did it all alone.

309
00:31:56,570 --> 00:31:58,491
The new book was published earlier.

310
00:32:01,370 --> 00:32:02,891
The body was found later.

311
00:32:06,491 --> 00:32:08,251
That day Li Meng called me.

312
00:32:08,850 --> 00:32:10,251
She wanted me to identify a pen.

313
00:32:10,570 --> 00:32:12,011
I'll send you some photos.

314
00:32:12,130 --> 00:32:14,370
(Li Meng)
See if any look familiar.

315
00:32:16,891 --> 00:32:17,451
Well?

316
00:32:17,770 --> 00:32:18,971
Any look familiar to you?

317
00:32:22,810 --> 00:32:24,251
From that day on,

318
00:32:25,370 --> 00:32:28,411
the exoneration chain formed in my mind.

319
00:32:31,011 --> 00:32:32,691
Your psychiatric report is out.

320
00:32:33,731 --> 00:32:34,411
You're not sick.

321
00:32:44,731 --> 00:32:46,251
Mom and Xiaofei are all set.

322
00:32:56,570 --> 00:32:57,770
Her testimony has loopholes.

323
00:33:00,610 --> 00:33:03,731
Autopsy shows the victim died
from a broken neck.

324
00:33:04,290 --> 00:33:07,330
But she never mentioned
how that fatal injury occurred.

325
00:33:08,290 --> 00:33:09,290
One more thing, Ma'am.

326
00:33:10,050 --> 00:33:12,011
If Zhou Na did have a knife

327
00:33:12,130 --> 00:33:15,171
and threaten Ren Xiaoming's
and Bai Shu's lives,

328
00:33:15,971 --> 00:33:17,651
what they did should be self-defense.

329
00:33:22,691 --> 00:33:25,290
No, Zhou Na couldn't have used a knife.

330
00:33:25,810 --> 00:33:26,451
Why?

331
00:33:27,251 --> 00:33:28,130
Because she had a gun.

332
00:33:30,584 --> 00:33:33,208
(2010, La City)

333
00:33:39,251 --> 00:33:40,451
(I'll kill her.)

334
00:33:40,691 --> 00:33:41,770
Who will you kill?

335
00:33:42,171 --> 00:33:45,211
Three years ago,
you checked into a hotel in Wuchuan.

336
00:33:45,691 --> 00:33:47,050
It's been three years.

337
00:33:47,691 --> 00:33:49,130
I thought you were over it now.

338
00:33:49,290 --> 00:33:50,530
I didn't expect you to meet up.

339
00:33:50,530 --> 00:33:52,891
If you keep talking nonsense,
I'll hit you right now.

340
00:33:54,050 --> 00:33:55,451
I've checked your account.

341
00:33:55,530 --> 00:33:57,050
You transferred 20,000 to that wretch.

342
00:34:00,011 --> 00:34:01,370
What do you take me for?

343
00:34:02,011 --> 00:34:03,610
Bai Shu is like a daughter to me.

344
00:34:04,330 --> 00:34:05,251
Am I a beast?

345
00:34:05,411 --> 00:34:07,731
Would I do such filthy things
with my daughter?

346
00:34:07,931 --> 00:34:09,011
Get out of here now.

347
00:34:09,530 --> 00:34:11,210
Hadn't you made a scene at the school,

348
00:34:11,530 --> 00:34:13,170
would Bai Shu be like this now?

349
00:34:15,331 --> 00:34:17,050
I really regret saving you back then.

350
00:34:20,130 --> 00:34:21,811
You should just die.

351
00:34:33,931 --> 00:34:34,891
Die!

352
00:34:37,931 --> 00:34:39,690
The bullet grazed my scalp.

353
00:34:41,250 --> 00:34:43,891
I woke up the next evening.

354
00:34:44,931 --> 00:34:45,971
And Zhou Na was gone.

355
00:34:46,530 --> 00:34:49,050
I called her, but her phone was off.

356
00:34:49,331 --> 00:34:51,650
I guess she might've thought I was dead.

357
00:34:52,170 --> 00:34:53,170
So she ran away.

358
00:34:55,090 --> 00:34:56,250
I rested for a few days.

359
00:34:57,570 --> 00:34:58,690
Then I went to Singapore.

360
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:00,170
Where'd Zhou Na get the gun?

361
00:35:02,411 --> 00:35:04,771
She used to work in casinos
in Southeast Asia.

362
00:35:05,050 --> 00:35:07,650
There were some very shady connections.

363
00:35:08,931 --> 00:35:10,690
Didn't Zhou Na's family look for you?

364
00:35:11,291 --> 00:35:13,811
I think there's one thing she said
that was very true.

365
00:35:14,971 --> 00:35:18,331
I might be the only person in this world
who cared about her life.

366
00:35:21,528 --> 00:35:24,320
(For ID card applications,
please use the side door)

367
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,090
What's the matter?

368
00:35:25,891 --> 00:35:26,811
To turn myself in.

369
00:35:27,250 --> 00:35:27,928
Come in.

370
00:35:30,891 --> 00:35:31,451
ID card.

371
00:35:38,331 --> 00:35:39,730
Criminal Investigation Unit,

372
00:35:40,011 --> 00:35:41,170
a woman turned herself in.

373
00:35:41,170 --> 00:35:41,891
Please come.

374
00:35:54,530 --> 00:35:55,130
Bai Shu?

375
00:35:57,411 --> 00:35:59,291
The murderer
in the Qidian Middle School case.

376
00:35:59,704 --> 00:36:00,530
I surrender myself.

377
00:36:05,690 --> 00:36:06,210
Bai Shu,

378
00:36:07,371 --> 00:36:09,730
you are now being questioned
according to the law.

379
00:36:10,570 --> 00:36:11,690
Have you found the diary?

380
00:36:12,130 --> 00:36:14,291
I can't answer that question.
Please cooperate.

381
00:36:15,411 --> 00:36:18,011
Are the diary and the novel
exactly the same?

382
00:36:18,491 --> 00:36:19,771
Explain your own issues.

383
00:36:20,411 --> 00:36:22,931
You can only find the truth
by doing as I say.

384
00:36:23,931 --> 00:36:25,291
On the diary's last few pages,

385
00:36:25,771 --> 00:36:27,331
I used coded writing

386
00:36:27,451 --> 00:36:29,451
to record the entire process
of killing Zhou Na.

387
00:36:32,891 --> 00:36:36,411
(In 2010, when I was burying the ashes
of the deceased in the back hill,)

388
00:36:37,011 --> 00:36:38,530
(2010)
(Zhou Na came to find me.)

389
00:36:38,530 --> 00:36:39,971
(Back hill of Rest Cemetery, Qidaohezi)

390
00:36:39,971 --> 00:36:42,011
(An unusual cold wave was coming.)

391
00:36:42,451 --> 00:36:44,331
(The wind started to turn cold.)

392
00:36:57,291 --> 00:36:58,170
I killed him.

393
00:36:59,050 --> 00:37:00,090
I killed Wang Hao.

394
00:37:01,570 --> 00:37:02,331
What did you say?

395
00:37:02,690 --> 00:37:03,690
I killed him.

396
00:37:04,050 --> 00:37:05,130
You killed Wang Hao?

397
00:37:09,891 --> 00:37:10,971
What's your plan?

398
00:37:11,971 --> 00:37:12,891
I don't know.

399
00:37:13,851 --> 00:37:15,291
I only have him now.

400
00:37:15,971 --> 00:37:17,050
He's the only one I have.

401
00:37:17,771 --> 00:37:19,130
But he's dead.

402
00:37:19,771 --> 00:37:20,851
I didn't mean to.

403
00:37:21,730 --> 00:37:23,011
He told me to die.

404
00:37:24,451 --> 00:37:25,650
He even hit me.

405
00:37:25,811 --> 00:37:27,331
I really didn't mean to.

406
00:37:32,331 --> 00:37:33,570
Why did you come to me?

407
00:37:34,250 --> 00:37:36,291
I used to hate you so much.

408
00:37:37,690 --> 00:37:38,971
I wanted to kill you.

409
00:37:40,250 --> 00:37:41,931
But now I don't want to kill anyone.

410
00:37:42,610 --> 00:37:45,371
I-I've never wanted to kill anyone.

411
00:37:45,371 --> 00:37:46,491
What should I do?

412
00:37:46,931 --> 00:37:49,411
Bai Shu, what should I do?

413
00:37:50,130 --> 00:37:50,771
Surrender.

414
00:37:51,291 --> 00:37:52,451
I don't want to surrender.

415
00:37:52,730 --> 00:37:54,411
You're trying to hurt me, aren't you?

416
00:37:54,530 --> 00:37:57,011
I don't want to be executed.
I don't want to surrender.

417
00:37:57,250 --> 00:37:58,570
If you really don't want to die,

418
00:37:58,931 --> 00:38:01,011
surrendering may reduce your sentence.

419
00:38:01,451 --> 00:38:02,491
You can still start over.

420
00:38:02,931 --> 00:38:04,411
- You vixen!
- (I told Zhou Na to surrender.)

421
00:38:04,411 --> 00:38:05,451
You're trying to harm me.

422
00:38:05,451 --> 00:38:07,491
(She grabbed me hysterically
and screamed.)

423
00:38:07,992 --> 00:38:08,650
(Suddenly,)

424
00:38:08,650 --> 00:38:10,250
- Bai Shu!
- (Ren Xiaoming appeared.)

425
00:38:10,371 --> 00:38:11,170
What are you doing?

426
00:38:11,170 --> 00:38:12,210
(She pushed Zhou Na away.)

427
00:38:13,090 --> 00:38:13,851
Are you okay?

428
00:38:14,011 --> 00:38:14,650
I'm fine.

429
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:16,130
I saw her sneaking around the street.

430
00:38:16,250 --> 00:38:17,371
I knew she'd come to you.

431
00:38:17,730 --> 00:38:18,610
Why are you here?

432
00:38:20,971 --> 00:38:23,451
What happens between you and him
is none of my business.

433
00:38:23,811 --> 00:38:26,411
About what you told me,
I won't tell anyone else.

434
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:38,650
Go.

435
00:38:43,130 --> 00:38:46,050
Blood. Where's this blood from?

436
00:38:48,090 --> 00:38:50,451
If you're going to leave,
leave completely.

437
00:38:50,891 --> 00:38:52,170
Never come back to me.

438
00:38:53,891 --> 00:38:54,451
Go.

439
00:39:06,690 --> 00:39:07,411
Go!

440
00:39:12,411 --> 00:39:15,570
(Suddenly, Zhou Na pulled out a gun
and fired at us.)

441
00:39:15,971 --> 00:39:16,891
(We were terrified)

442
00:39:17,210 --> 00:39:18,371
- Run!
- (and fled.)

443
00:39:19,130 --> 00:39:21,411
(Zhou Na was chasing us relentlessly
with a gun in hand.)

444
00:39:35,250 --> 00:39:36,851
Xiaoming, let's split up

445
00:39:37,090 --> 00:39:38,090
and find a place to hide.

446
00:39:39,411 --> 00:39:40,891
We'll meet up later. Hurry!

447
00:39:41,971 --> 00:39:44,811
(The forest was vast,
and the fog that day was heavy.)

448
00:39:45,851 --> 00:39:48,210
(Running and running,
we somehow ended up back)

449
00:39:48,491 --> 00:39:49,690
(where we started.)

450
00:40:07,570 --> 00:40:09,170
(Suddenly, I realized)

451
00:40:09,291 --> 00:40:12,170
(Zhou Na was pointing a gun
at Xiaoming from behind.)

452
00:40:25,931 --> 00:40:27,931
(Zhou Na pressed the gun
against her forehead.)

453
00:40:28,451 --> 00:40:30,250
(Just as Zhou Na pulled the trigger,)

454
00:40:30,690 --> 00:40:32,530
(I stabbed her neck with the pen.)

455
00:40:37,210 --> 00:40:38,250
Let's go.

456
00:40:38,371 --> 00:40:39,291
Hurry.

457
00:40:39,411 --> 00:40:40,530
(Did she die on the spot?)

458
00:40:40,771 --> 00:40:43,491
(No, she was still chasing us
with the gun.)

459
00:40:43,730 --> 00:40:44,690
We were both terrified.

460
00:40:45,411 --> 00:40:47,291
We just kept running and running.

461
00:40:48,851 --> 00:40:50,971
We didn't stop
until we got out of the back hill.

462
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:55,411
Is she dead?

463
00:40:55,650 --> 00:40:57,570
No, she was still chasing us.

464
00:40:57,891 --> 00:40:59,730
- Let's go.
- Let's go back and check.

465
00:41:00,491 --> 00:41:01,451
Don't. It's dangerous.

466
00:41:01,610 --> 00:41:03,384
She has a gun. Let's go.

467
00:41:08,371 --> 00:41:09,730
(Ren Xiaoming got a phone call.)

468
00:41:10,170 --> 00:41:12,811
She left in a hurry
right after the call.

469
00:41:14,170 --> 00:41:15,650
It scared me more the more I thought.

470
00:41:16,050 --> 00:41:16,971
I feared she was dead.

471
00:41:17,491 --> 00:41:18,570
I chose to return to check.

472
00:41:32,491 --> 00:41:35,090
(Are you sure
about the cause of Zhou Na's death?)

473
00:41:35,331 --> 00:41:36,050
I'm sure.

474
00:41:37,210 --> 00:41:39,011
Zhou Na had no other wounds on her body.

475
00:41:39,451 --> 00:41:42,130
The blood spurted from her neck.

476
00:41:42,771 --> 00:41:45,491
I think I must've hit
her carotid artery.

477
00:41:45,891 --> 00:41:47,011
Why not call the police?

478
00:41:51,711 --> 00:41:53,011
(I was about to call the police)

479
00:41:53,610 --> 00:41:55,931
(when I suddenly
noticed something very strange.)

480
00:42:00,491 --> 00:42:02,971
(The gun that had been
in Zhou Na's hand was gone.)

481
00:42:10,530 --> 00:42:13,130
(I was horrified.
There was no one around.)

482
00:42:21,050 --> 00:42:22,730
The gun was gone. Someone took it.

483
00:42:23,170 --> 00:42:25,891
That person was likely the eyewitness
to the entire incident.

484
00:42:26,610 --> 00:42:28,331
The gun, the eyewitness,

485
00:42:28,851 --> 00:42:29,931
and their testimony

486
00:42:30,291 --> 00:42:31,170
were three variables.

487
00:42:31,672 --> 00:42:33,208
Whether the police could find the gun

488
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,971
or the eyewitness

489
00:42:35,411 --> 00:42:37,971
and whether their testimony
was favorable to us

490
00:42:39,090 --> 00:42:40,530
were all variables within variables.

491
00:42:41,011 --> 00:42:42,331
Among these variables,

492
00:42:42,771 --> 00:42:44,011
there's only one combination.

493
00:42:45,291 --> 00:42:48,130
You found the gun and the eyewitness,

494
00:42:49,411 --> 00:42:52,130
and the eyewitness admitted
to illegally taking the gun

495
00:42:52,690 --> 00:42:55,491
and honestly told you
everything they saw.

496
00:42:57,491 --> 00:42:58,931
Only this combination

497
00:42:59,210 --> 00:43:01,771
could prove we acted in self-defense.

498
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
